text: Ahmed Tijan Janko (born 28 April 1995) is a Qatari beach volleyball player originally from Gambia. In 2018, he alongside Cherif Younousse clinched the gold medal at the 2018 Asian Games in Palembang, Indonesia. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:People from Banjul Category:Qatari beach volleyball players Category:Asian Games gold medalists for Qatar Category:Asian Games medalists in beach volleyball Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Beach volleyball players at the 2018 Asian Games
